{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/docker_1","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"a0bc069f-c7c8-5e48-b063-7adb829b6c09","html":"<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 960px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/581f1ab869f8381570f595a32d9640c1/1843f/docker_essential.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.25%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/581f1ab869f8381570f595a32d9640c1/8ac56/docker_essential.webp 240w,\n/static/581f1ab869f8381570f595a32d9640c1/d3be9/docker_essential.webp 480w,\n/static/581f1ab869f8381570f595a32d9640c1/e46b2/docker_essential.webp 960w,\n/static/581f1ab869f8381570f595a32d9640c1/f52fe/docker_essential.webp 1186w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/581f1ab869f8381570f595a32d9640c1/8ff5a/docker_essential.png 240w,\n/static/581f1ab869f8381570f595a32d9640c1/e85cb/docker_essential.png 480w,\n/static/581f1ab869f8381570f595a32d9640c1/d9199/docker_essential.png 960w,\n/static/581f1ab869f8381570f595a32d9640c1/1843f/docker_essential.png 1186w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n          type=\"image/png\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/581f1ab869f8381570f595a32d9640c1/d9199/docker_essential.png\"\n          alt=\"img\"\n          title=\"img\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Docker 이미지를 만들고, 이를 Amazon ECR에 배포하는 과정을 정리해 보았다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"1-docker-image-build-하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-docker-image-build-%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"1 docker image build 하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. Docker image build 하기</h3>\n<p>Docker image는 이미지를 생성하는 지점에 <code class=\"language-text\">Dockerfile</code> 을 작성해두고, cli에서 다음 command를 입력한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">$ docker build -t <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>image name<span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">.</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>이후 <code class=\"language-text\">docker images</code> command를 입력하면 이미지 리스트가 나온다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"2-이미지-tag-naming\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-%EC%9D%B4%EB%AF%B8%EC%A7%80-tag-naming\" aria-label=\"2 이미지 tag naming permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. 이미지 tag naming</h3>\n<p>ECR에 배포할 docker image로 바꿔주기 위해서는 image의 name, tag를 바꾸어 주어야 한다. 다음 command를 입력한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">$ docker tag <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>oldbie image name<span class=\"token operator\">></span>:latest XXX.dkr.ecr.ap-northeast-2.com/<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>newbie image name<span class=\"token operator\">></span>:<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>tag stage<span class=\"token operator\">></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>이후 <code class=\"language-text\">docker images</code> command를 다시 입력하면 변경된 태그로 새 이미지가 추가된 것을 확인할 수 있다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"3-ecr에-이미지-배포하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-ecr%EC%97%90-%EC%9D%B4%EB%AF%B8%EC%A7%80-%EB%B0%B0%ED%8F%AC%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"3 ecr에 이미지 배포하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. ECR에 이미지 배포하기</h3>\n<p>Docker에 이미지를 배포하기 이전에, 우선 AWS ECR에 로그인에 성공해야 한다.\n먼저 AWS IAM에서 ECR의 접근 권한을 포함한 access_key, password를 발급받는다.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>~/.aws/credentials</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">[keyset]\naws_access_key_id = XXX\naws_secret_access_key = XXX</code></pre></div>\n<p>이후에 다음 command로 AWS docker ECR에 로그인한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">$ aws ecr get-login-password --region ap-northeast-2 <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> \ndocker login --username AWS --password-stdin XXX.dkr.ecr.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com</code></pre></div>\n<p>이후에는 docker cli에 <code class=\"language-text\">XXX.dkr.ecr.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com</code>에 로그인이 완료된 상태로, 다음과 같이 이미지를 배포해주면 된다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">$ docker push XXX.dkr.ecr.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>image name<span class=\"token operator\">></span>:<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>stage tag<span class=\"token operator\">></span></code></pre></div>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/docker_1","tagSlugs":["/tag/docker/","/tag/amazon-ecr/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2021-06-20T23:00:00.000Z","description":"docker의 기본적인 명령어 정리, docker image를 amazon ECR에 배포하기","tags":["docker","amazon ecr"],"title":"Docker Essentials","socialImage":{"publicURL":"/static/581f1ab869f8381570f595a32d9640c1/docker_essential.png"}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/docker_1"}},"staticQueryHashes":["251939775","401334301","825871152"]}